From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: wosnxn123 <wosnxn123@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Sat, 4 Jul 2026 23:50:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add Vanilla-like experience config

Adds config/canvas-server.yml -> vanilla-like-experience.enabled master
toggle restoring vanilla mechanics Paper/Folia changed (tripwire string
farms, TNT/sand duping, permanent block break, headless pistons, vanilla
mob spawning, unlimited entity collisions, player cramming, vanilla
phantom behavior, no TNT limit, vanilla hopper/bee/item-merge/end-portal
teleport). When disabled, Paper per-mechanic configs apply as normal.
Ported from LuminolMC/Lophine 0048, adapted to Canvas GlobalConfiguration
+ Canvas pre-merger/26.2 NMS context. Patch regenerated via git diff on
Canvas pre-merger/26.2 applied source (correct blob index + context).

